        <abstract>
            <p>Pleased with JDH’s account of his French tour.</p>
            <p>Doctor Brinton, recommended by Busk, does not believe CD’s brain or heart affected. Feels he is going steadily downhill. If so, hopes his life will be short.</p>
            <p>Sends Haast’s letter.</p>
        </abstract>
